				<p>I translate and proof-read essays, articles, projects, presentations, websites, and anything in textual form. If you need to translate a text, or have it proof-read, don’t hesitate to contact me.</p>
				
				<h4>I offer:</h4>
				
				<ul>
					<li>Translation services,</li>
					<li>Proofreading,</li>
					<li>Tutoring*</li>
				</ul>
				
				<p>I translate from Italian, English and Greek to the languages in which I’m bilingual: English and Greek</p>
				
				<ul>
					<li>Italian ⟶ English</li>
					<li>Greek ⟷ English</li>
					<li>Italian ⟶ Greek</li>
				</ul>
				
				<p>I mainly work with academic texts (scientific articles, essays and theses of all university levels) and have experience in diverse fields, from design and anthropology to physics. At the same time, I work on texts targeted to a wider audience, in sectors such as tourism.</p>
				
				<h4>Examples of texts</h4>
				
				<ul>
					<li>Proposals and abstracts</li>
					<li>Motivation letters</li>
					<li>Presentations (for seminars, conferences etc)</li>
					<li>Statements</li>
					<li>Guides</li>
					<li>Scientific articles</li>
					<li>Journalism articles / blogs</li>
					<li>Theses and essays</li>
					<li>Literature</li>
					<li>Websites</li>
				</ul>
				
				<small><p>* As an English as a Second Language teacher, in addition to conversation-based classes, I offer tutoring and preparation services for interviews and presentations.</p></small>
				
